1. Kupili smo novu *opremu* za našu radionicu. (We bought new equipment for our workshop.)
2. *Opremu* za vožnju bicikla treba redovno servisirati. (The equipment for cycling needs to be serviced regularly.)
3. Ona je investirala u sofisticiranu *opremu*. (She has invested in sophisticated equipment.)
4. *Opremu* za lov na ribu treba prilagođavati vremenskim prilikama. (The fishing equipment should be adapted to the weather conditions.)
5. Oni su obnovili svoju *opremu* za skijanje. (They renewed their skiing equipment.)